<svg class="ee-diagram" role="img" aria-label="An incident, a quiet sense that there is more here, and a fork: connect, or dismiss." preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid meet" viewBox="0 0 680 360" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
